<paragraph base="F29577379" principles="yes" id="IFRS14_6"><paranum>6</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 14"/><data name="paranum" value="6"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS14_P0021">An entity shall apply the requirements of this Standard in its financial statements              for subsequent periods if and only if, in its <xref base="F29577610" href="IFRS14_APPA.dita#IFRS14_APPA/IFRS14_DI0001" scope="local">first IFRS financial statements<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0133"/></ph></xref>, it recognised <xref base="F29577655" href="IFRS14_APPA.dita#IFRS14_APPA/IFRS14_DI0007" scope="local">regulatory deferral account balances<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0321"/></ph></xref> by electing to apply the requirements of this Standard.</p></body></paragraph>